程序包 map

类 MapListing

java.lang.Object
map.MapDetailAccess
map.MapListing
public class MapListing
extends MapDetailAccess
This class is to get some lists and correspondence from the map file Including: the continent list, the total country list , the country list from a continent and the list of neighbour countries.
版本:
1.0.0
作者:
Zitao Wang
